*Most Consecutive Games With a TD Pass &mdash; 15 (from December 3, 2006 through November 18, 2007)
*Most 4th Quarter Comeback Wins &mdash; 19 (tied with [[Terry Bradshaw]])
*Most Games with a Passer Rating over 100.0 (regular season; min. 10 attempts) &mdash; 42<ref>[http://www.pro-football-reference.com/play-index/tiny/vtuCd "Player Game Finder Query Results"] Pro-Football-Reference.com</ref>
